# EDSDK v13.13.0 (Placeholder)

This directory is a placeholder for Canon EDSDK version 13.13.0.

## Compatible Cameras

- EOS 550D
- EOS 600D  
- EOS 650D
- EOS 700D
- EOS 60D
- EOS 7D
- EOS 5D Mark II
- EOS 5D Mark III

## Installation

1. Download Canon EDSDK v13.13.0 from Canon's developer website
2. Extract the Windows 64-bit DLL files to this directory:
   - `EDSDK.dll`
   - `EdsImage.dll`
   - `DPP4Lib/` (if present)

## Note

This is an older SDK version maintained for compatibility with legacy Canon cameras.
For modern cameras (EOS R series, 90D, 850D, 250D), use v13.20.10 instead.
